{"tid":1298163,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[新會員入] 連登第一個新手教學!","createTime":"2019-07-08T19:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:08:01.000Z","uid":139605,"like":140,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae8f1a19804619092f8158ccc7090cf1fbf2283","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:54:58.000Z","msg":"鑑於今晚有會員玩假膠<br />\n而導致有新嚟巴絲同同路人好不幸被fake<br />\n我決定出個新手教學比大家<br />\n等大家容易啲融入連登呢個大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申定先 我都唔係玩左好耐連登 <br />\n坦白講有啲野我都未明得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以有錯希望大家細力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋比下意見新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">終極懶人包:睇連登一定要有獨立思考!千其唔好連登仔講咩信咩!</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n原因一:其實連登有大量三毛<br />\n<br />\n當中仲有三毛好敬業 <br />\n出嘅po好似好有point 但認真諗就會發現唔對路<br />\n例如 尋日有人叫人唔好再扮記者 話會連累記者<br />\n但細心諗下就會發現明明都無人扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又何來&quot;再&quot;呢<br />\n明顯係想屈示威者<br />\n<br />\n又有堆三毛負責comment帶風向<br />\n例如今晚假膠事件發生之後<br />\n有一大堆ac沖出嚟話以後都唔再出嚟<br />\n係咪真係五毛我唔敢講<br />\n但以我認識嘅香港人(仲要講緊呢班人係好有心 願意為香港係夜晚話出嚟就出嚟)係唔似會被人fake一次就以後都唔嚟<br />\n<br />\n至於有無實質方法辨認三毛 我只可以講無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂最直觀嘅方法都係睇id no.<br />\n基本上24字頭打後嘅no. 係三毛嘅機會會大少少<br />\n(雖然入得嚟睇嘅巴絲都應該係25 26 打後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n就算係靠前嘅no.都可以係三毛嚟<br />\n所以最實際都係自己思考下<br />\n由言論去判斷係咪三毛<br />\n另外時事台有個三毛list 巴絲信唔過自己可以去跟住嚟block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因二:連登有假膠<br />\n<br />\n假膠其實都算係連登主要文化嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時係講緊多幾倍假膠<br />\n不過呢個月大家都好認真做正經野先無假膠<br />\n結果一玩膠就玩埋自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而最盞鬼嘅係 每個連登仔都可以係假膠<br />\n就算我呢刻出認真po 我下個po都可以係假膠嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到底 連登仔只係一個代號嚟<br />\n係真實世界到底係邊個人 <br />\n係同路人定三毛 就咁睇個ac係睇唔出<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以以下幾點好重要:<br />\n1.一定要經過自己思考去決定可唔可信!<br />\n2.唔清楚就唔好咁快下定論<br />\nFact check /google左先!<br />\n3.唔好盲目相信正負評!</span><br />\n<br />\n跟住落嚟我會講下幾個連登主要文化<br />\n<br />\n1.假膠<br />\n相信大家經過今晚之後都對假膠有基本嘅認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先 假膠其實有好多種 解密只係其中一個<br />\n除此之外仲有&quot;我公司個90後&quot;系列 &quot;夠500/1000正評就裸跑/派錢etc.&quot;系列<br />\n呢度詳細就唔多講 大家有興趣可以得閒search嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此外仲有好多 <br />\n近期少少嘅有萎萎撐反送中事件<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />in case仲有人唔知 唯唯無反送中 佢重頭到尾都好愛國的 大家唔好咁多幻想<br />\n成件事由頭到尾都無發生過<br />\n但因為多人講 三人成虎 就好多人信<br />\n對呢種無中生有類嘅假膠 (其實所有假膠都係)<br />\n記得獨立思考就可以了<br />\n例子:<br />\nFact:萎萎好耐之前已經北上靠奶共上位<br />\n絕對無可能反送中<br />\nQ.咁點解連登仔話佢反送中?<br />\nA.想搞到萎萎雞毛鴨血 比大陸人罵<br />\n大概係咁<br />\n<br />\n2.曲線<br />\n簡單嚟講即係高級版嘅講反話 <br />\n如果見到非連登主流意見嘅po<br />\n(如支持警察 拉晒示威者坐監 etc.)<br />\n建議望多幾頁先下定論<br />\n一般呢種po好快就會有人/樓主自己忍唔住爆響口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一般嚟講曲線po一係多正皮一係多負皮<br />\n意思大概係:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曲線諷刺又搞笑 大家都get到笑位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曲得太假 又唔好笑又無point<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />曲得太真 大家點知係咪狗/藍絲<br />\n大概係咁 但都係個句 <br />\n正負皮唔可以代表任何野<br />\n好嘅曲線都可以因為太好而比真心膠負皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到呢度先 希望其他巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407a88a563c09991527e2bd292e3d594245b8a3b","tid":1298163,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:55:55.000Z","msg":"睡前讀物 入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「有圖」連儂牆係建制派叫人嚟拆嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298148\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298148</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"5c703bf0f5bdd07333dc39f2627c472ef25e393b","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:56:14.000Z","msg":"啱先開左係公海<br />\n受巴打指點開多次係學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775dfc42aa8e9b18ef798c39f7de55ce8d9f6e94","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:58:01.000Z","msg":"可以的話其實想搞個page<br />\n方便新巴絲睇<br />\n但樓豬乜都唔識<br />\n唯有開住po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d889f7502460e1e48c0f0002d871219c7ac700b","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:00:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"d360f0d380d6a26ef1af4837ea9fbacfa5d02d4b","tid":1298163,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:05:55.000Z","msg":"新手廢中入嚟學野..<br />\n<br />\n暫時覺得最有效係起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff748c5f4ca77e17bc51df806e78f6b86310c5ce","tid":1298163,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:08:00.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講即係高登嘅劣版<br />\n小丑神萬歲<br />\n腦魔萬歲"},{"pid":"dcbb19dd954441c34d2a35349a12f0bbfa7900e1","tid":1298163,"uid":262435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:14:01.000Z","msg":"推 新會言真係唔好信曬連登仔<br />\n再加埋宜家好多5毛<br />\n凡事都盡量fact check左先<br />\n另外代其他ON9連登仔代各位say個sorry<br />\n佢地今次真係過份左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dc2a694166d16d5958220537d976c10135e26b","tid":1298163,"uid":51760,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012d2c30a2ecd86af6556d14b314ac922a86672f","tid":1298163,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3bcbb04e2d7182bcf53356de9e4e9acde21f8f","tid":1298163,"uid":245523,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"正皮多亦唔代表啱<br />\n例如嗰個叫人唔好著黑衫嘅post今日有成千正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重複多次 著黑衫全民black block係為咗cover勇武 如果變咗黑衫=勇武而搞到其他人唔跟嘅話 只會累死前線手足<br />\n<br />\n再者 依家黑色已經有種象徵係度 去遊行集會大家係地鐵巴士見到成車黑衫個心都舒服啲 營造一個團結 整體嘅氣氛 用咗一個月先令大家有著黑衫呢個意識 唔會隨便搵條友岀post就可以打回原型<br />\n<br />\n另外 連登反對5p字（除非玩膠）雖然依家處於戰時冇乜人屌 不過最後都係唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n❌系 ✔️係<br />\n❌吾 ✔️唔<br />\n❌甘 ✔️咁<br />\n❌牙 ✔️呀"},{"pid":"a2f004eb55692b8913d04c0352ff4e7e34984344","tid":1298163,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:28:10.000Z","msg":"假膠真係好撚煩<br />\n我好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4961bfacc0c5ea464d520a2fb71fba4c15dc8e06","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:30:58.000Z","msg":"PISH<br />\n其實舊會然一睇就知係玩膠POST<br />\n只係俾五毛利用左成功帶風向<br />\n用連登一定要起底同埋要有獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n通常五毛有幾樣特徵：<br />\n1.一定唔會屌建制<br />\n2.曲線吹奏中共 話中共好撚勁你地點打得贏<br />\n3.散播失敗主義<br />\n4.成日叫人散<br />\n5.大中華膠<br />\n6.拉一派打一派<br />\n<br />\n起底：<br />\n1.POST文間隔太長 有可能買AC<br />\n2.新會然<br />\n3.睇佢D PO出咩文多"},{"pid":"1539260263a6d310b83822f07e8746ac46154f00","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d3bcbb04e2d7182bcf53356de9e4e9acde21f8f","tid":1298163,"uid":245523,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"正皮多亦唔代表啱<br />\n例如嗰個叫人唔好著黑衫嘅post今日有成千正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重複多次 著黑衫全民black block係為咗cover勇武 如果變咗黑衫=勇武而搞到其他人唔跟嘅話 只會累死前線手足<br />\n<br />\n再者 依家黑色已經有種象徵係度 去遊行集會大家係地鐵巴士見到成車黑衫個心都舒服啲 營造一個團結 整體嘅氣氛 用咗一個月先令大家有著黑衫呢個意識 唔會隨便搵條友岀post就可以打回原型<br />\n<br />\n另外 連登反對5p字（除非玩膠）雖然依家處於戰時冇乜人屌 不過最後都係唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n❌系 ✔️係<br />\n❌吾 ✔️唔<br />\n❌甘 ✔️咁<br />\n❌牙 ✔️呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:31:44.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220cdb7b857a01ced23c934fb26f91a7fbd1b932","tid":1298163,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1539260263a6d310b83822f07e8746ac46154f00","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d3bcbb04e2d7182bcf53356de9e4e9acde21f8f","tid":1298163,"uid":245523,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:26:24.000Z","msg":"正皮多亦唔代表啱<br />\n例如嗰個叫人唔好著黑衫嘅post今日有成千正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重複多次 著黑衫全民black block係為咗cover勇武 如果變咗黑衫=勇武而搞到其他人唔跟嘅話 只會累死前線手足<br />\n<br />\n再者 依家黑色已經有種象徵係度 去遊行集會大家係地鐵巴士見到成車黑衫個心都舒服啲 營造一個團結 整體嘅氣氛 用咗一個月先令大家有著黑衫呢個意識 唔會隨便搵條友岀post就可以打回原型<br />\n<br />\n另外 連登反對5p字（除非玩膠）雖然依家處於戰時冇乜人屌 不過最後都係唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n❌系 ✔️係<br />\n❌吾 ✔️唔<br />\n❌甘 ✔️咁<br />\n❌牙 ✔️呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:31:44.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:34:34.000Z","msg":"費事之後有新會員唔知頭唔知路無辜被屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d820770e7267f29019c867ceba9b309b0a8948","tid":1298163,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d799b3add1ca2dffdb55bef85faf84c7a03f06","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論見到乜撚野POST起左底先</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1cb84bf713e148f5f44c332da2045d83e696c8d","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4addd659113fb3045532a3afa842a9211bc526","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔記得講<br />\n深夜其實好撚柒鳩多五毛係度不停推POST上去<br />\n企圖令朝早班人情報混淆<br />\n例如77之前有單武漢垃圾場<br />\n班五毛真係同你KEEP住推文<br />\n而家潛撚哂水"},{"pid":"f2cf6554ecc8744d5e81ce0379f800bc71779838","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:56:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我相信之後一定有分化撚係度推玩膠POST上黎<br />\n禁最後一頁睇下推POST係咪個幾條友"},{"pid":"e60e6e742a6ff99506538b8045169451b69e765c","tid":1298163,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74937cce3fd5e9d9b48a01091a1489e3313b3146","tid":1298163,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"港共成功左 由得我地和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n你地開始玩膠，即係證明你地不再憤怒，覺得好開心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1298176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1298176</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb4d5fb627f4b814c05c4520b5514301f5ca8477","tid":1298163,"uid":77484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7ba000c89c497f8e401b4e118f53dd36a51e826","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n<code>我無野講</code>"},{"pid":"d06336fd6dc0099ea9c45e72adaeb467cab8ffcd","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:39:44.000Z","msg":"係熱門見到呢個po 就想講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【怪錯好人】長洲撕連儂牆日本人姨姨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299127</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n利申先 唔討論真相係點 淨係講連登現象<br />\n呢個po一眼望落去好多正皮<br />\n但comment就起碼一半都罵緊<br />\n再睇翻一樓<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">樓主重頭到尾都得個up字<br />\n無source亦無圖support佢講嘅野</span><br />\n所以比眾多連登仔質疑<br />\n直到幾頁之後 有人po左老闆寫支持反送中嘅板 大家先開始信<br />\n由呢個po睇到 <span style=\"color: red;\">有圖/source有真相 無圖勿輕信</span><br />\n當然講就咁講 有時即使有相都唔代表真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要當然係獨立思考</span><br />\n<br />\n另外想講下正負皮<br />\n上面個po咁多人罵 點解有咁多正皮?<br />\n<br />\n原因一 部分會員無經思考而相信樓主<br />\n所以想正皮 還老闆清白<br />\n<br />\n原因二 部分會員盲目相信正負皮 <br />\n見到個po好多人正皮 <br />\n所以就正皮左先再睇文<br />\n甚至因為正皮而影響自己嘅判斷<br />\n<br />\n事實上即使係我 係碌連登comment個陣<br />\n第一眼都忍唔住睇正負皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禁完正皮再睇文 先發現比錯左正皮嘅情況都成日發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其呢個月非常時期 都試過好幾次正皮完後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以絕對唔可以盲目相信正負皮</span>"},{"pid":"5b6f2673ce609a98c446154289a5eaf209e16ab4","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"btw 歡迎各位發問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我識嘅就盡答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d2f9d2da006677f5d46abd53045071e78c458e","tid":1298163,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"總之起底功能好重要"},{"pid":"5d495d9550d1db1bbe6f174d4419c8da53f4961e","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb4d5fb627f4b814c05c4520b5514301f5ca8477","tid":1298163,"uid":77484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"我都估唔到我會開呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到尋晚有巴絲信假膠 搞到出左金鐘<br />\n曲線po又被瘋狂負皮<br />\n就知道其實好多同路人根本唔熟連登文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想出個教學等佢地唔好再中伏"},{"pid":"42bf41752c546859e73f593fdf052c4ee429267c","tid":1298163,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"309c087587f85d3dce6e16592aafd0d2c3d2c81f","tid":1298163,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3300c8773b21cd3972ddb292ff15d7457bc7c6d","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">善用起底功能</span>都好重要<br />\n尤其係遇到所謂敬業三毛 講嘅野真假難分嘅時候<br />\n起底可以見到三毛開嘅其他po<br />\n其他po嘅comment 正負皮數<br />\nac no.前後等等<br />\n結合埋就比較容易識穿三毛"},{"pid":"6401c75c2ed7c43472526090b9dcd906746cacce","tid":1298163,"uid":179144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑咗，上連登都要有教學post<br />\n尋晚我條女都俾兒登仔fake咗，叫晒救命call我出去，我答佢：假架啲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c29445f7585013f280cf717dd848a1353e7157","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6401c75c2ed7c43472526090b9dcd906746cacce","tid":1298163,"uid":179144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑咗，上連登都要有教學post<br />\n尋晚我條女都俾兒登仔fake咗，叫晒救命call我出去，我答佢：假架啲奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排真係多左好多新會員/cd rom<br />\n呢個時候嚟得嘅都係同路人(三毛除外)<br />\n見佢地比假膠fake到出金鐘真係好慘<br />\n希望教學幫到佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ab956a154ea7b049bb52c7cd19b06f8760b5a0","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQdQ92x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQdQ92x.png&h=757366d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連暫