要換/換左都無用<br />\n但要知道警犬真係唔係人嚟<br />\n係會進化到見到黑衫就查證<br />\n再chok多兩chok 見你開始緊張 <br />\n就塔埋你翻去48<br />\n所以要帶衫換 有能力的話可以帶多幾件嚟比其他無帶衫嘅巴絲/做面罩"},{"pid":"c9c6ac5709377ab661ad72d5f7165cbba500983a","tid":1298163,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"P仔想問, 點知有人回覆了自己的 Post?"},{"pid":"3b80a3bfc2ed1357853c6a370329134ff17e35af","tid":1298163,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7e23a7a1e26645a4434c7bfafb2ce01f713de51","tid":1298163,"uid":139605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9c6ac5709377ab661ad72d5f7165cbba500983a","tid":1298163,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"P仔想問, 點知有人回覆了自己的 Post?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"係主頁 左向右拉<br />\n會出到簡唔同台個panel<br />\n左下有幾個灰色制 第一個係鐘<br />\n有回覆會見到個鐘有紅色一字<br />\n禁入去就見到邊個覆你了"},{"pid":"caf9a1bda01d56868c3d8bc69098e50dbc772acb","tid":1298163,"uid":284989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7d799b3add1ca2dffdb55bef85faf84c7a03f06","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論見到乜撚野POST起左底先</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"低能問題：點起？"},{"pid":"8befbc44c232802167860a9e43f2685377740fac","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caf9a1bda01d56868c3d8bc69098e50dbc772acb","tid":1298163,"uid":284989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7d799b3add1ca2dffdb55bef85faf84c7a03f06","tid":1298163,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論見到乜撚野POST起左底先</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"低能問題：點起？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T1